          <article class="post-type-page" id="article">
            
          <div class="intro-text">

                      <h1 class="_title post-title">Center for Tax Law &amp; Employee Benefits</h1>
              
            
              
    
        
  </div>
        <div class="components">

  
    
      

<section class="component  ">

  
  <div class="component-text-block">
  
    <div class="component-description">
                    <h2 id="welcome" class="__title invisible">Welcome</h2>
                    </div>

    <figure class="_image captioned-image image-left-half">
  <img src="https://jmls.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/492/2020/02/taxlaw-center-1.jpg" alt="Kathryn J. Kennedy Professor of Law Director, Center for Tax Law &amp; Employee Benefits">
  </figure>
  
  <h3>Our Mission</h3>
<p>The Center for Tax Law &amp; Employee Benefits is dedicated to offering graduate degrees with rigorous academic standards, fostering research for better understanding of the multi-disciplinary aspects of the law, encouraging student participation in relevant bar association committees, and hosting topical forums to educate the bar and the community.</p>



  
</div>

  
</section>

    

    
      

<section class="component  ">

  
      <div class="component-multi-column-text">

        
    <div class="component-description">
                    <h2 id="degree-programs" class="__title visible">Degree Programs</h2>
                    </div>

        <div class="component-multi-column-text__columns">
            
                <div class="component-multi-column-text__column component-multi-column-text__column--two">

                                            <h3 id="jd-programs" class="component-multi-column-text__column__title visible">
                          JD Programs
                        </h3>
                    
                    
                    <div class="component-multi-column-text__content">
                        <ul>
<li><strong><a href="/academics/centers/taxeb/jd-llm-eb/">Joint JD/LLM in Employee Benefits</a><br />
</strong>Develop expertise in the increasingly complex field of employee benefits.</li>
<li><a href="/academics/centers/taxeb/jd-llm-estateplanning/"><strong>Joint JD/LLM in Estate Planning</strong></a><br />
Distinguish yourself in the estate planning arena.</li>
<li><a href="/academics/centers/taxeb/jd-llm-taxlaw/"><strong>Joint JD/LLM in Tax Law</strong></a><br />
Enhance your marketability in the area of federal income tax.</li>
</ul>
<div>
<div></div>
</div>

                    </div>

                                    </div>

            
                <div class="component-multi-column-text__column component-multi-column-text__column--two">

                                            <h3 id="llm-mj-programs" class="component-multi-column-text__column__title visible">
                          LLM &amp; MJ Programs
                        </h3>
                    
                    
                    <div class="component-multi-column-text__content">
                        <ul>
<li><a href="/academics/centers/taxeb/llm-eb/"><strong>LLM in Employee Benefits*</strong></a>
<div>
<div>
<div><em>(for practicing attorneys)</em></div>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div> Develop the skills necessary to successfully practice in the field of employee benefits.</div>
</div>
</li>
<li><a href="/academics/centers/taxeb/mj-eb/"><strong>MJ in Employee Benefits*</strong></a><br />
<em>(for non-attorney professionals)</em><br />
Expand your career opportunities with the practical competencies we offer our LLM candidates, without the law degree.</li>
<li><a href="/academics/centers/taxeb/llm-estateplanning/"><strong>LLM in Estate Planning*</strong></a>
<div>
<div>
<div><em>(for practicing attorneys)</em></div>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>Develop expertise in the estate planning arena.</div>
</div>
</li>
<li><a href="/academics/centers/taxeb/mj-estateplanning/"><strong>MJ in Estate Planning*</strong></a><br />
<em>(for non-attorney professionals)<br />
</em>Master the transactions that best suit your clients’ estates, without the law degree.</li>
<li><a href="/academics/centers/taxeb/llm-taxlaw/"><strong>LLM in Tax Law</strong></a>
<div>
<div>
<div><em>(for practicing attorneys)</em></div>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div> Expand your career opportunities with transactional training in tax law.</div>
</div>
</li>
<li><a href="/academics/centers/taxeb/mj-taxlaw/"><strong>MJ in Tax Law</strong></a><br />
<em>(for non-attorney professionals)<br />
</em>Distinguish your career with the same competencies we offer our LLM candidates, without the law degree.</li>
</ul>
<p><em>*Online courses and degrees are also available</em></p>

                    </div>

                                    </div>

                    </div>
    </div>

  
</section>

    

</div>

          </article>
        </div>

                                            
                                 
              
                            
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   




   
                                 
              
                            
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   




   




   
                                 
              
                            
                                 
              
                            
                                 
              
                            




   




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   
                                 
              
                            




   




   
                                 
              

